==事前準備==
美國和[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]協調的停火屆滿後，2016年9月19日起，敘利亞空軍恢復空襲[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]的反對派控制區，為即將來臨的地面攻勢鋪路。敘利亞空軍曾在一夜間對「征服阿勒頗」控制的5個地區進行超過40次的空襲。<ref name="ahead">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-jets-pound-east-aleppo-ahead-upcoming-offensive/|author=News Desk|publisher=almasdarnews.com|title=Syrian jets pound east Aleppo ahead of upcoming offensive|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617110042/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-jets-pound-east-aleppo-ahead-upcoming-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="second">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/sep/22/syria-army-new-aleppo-offensive-ceasefire |publisher=theguardian.com |title=Aleppo enters second day of bombing in new Syrian army offensive |accessdate=2016-09-23 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414032418/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/sep/22/syria-army-new-aleppo-offensive-ceasefire |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==攻勢==
2016年9月22日，[[叙利亚武装力量|敘利亞軍方]]宣佈恢復在阿勒頗的攻勢。<ref>[http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-23/8013036.shtml 叙利亚军方宣布恢复阿勒颇攻势] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-23/8013036.shtml |date=20200427130819 }}，中新網，2016-09-23</ref>

9月23日，敘軍在阿勒頗市南郊發起地面攻勢。<ref>[http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=51049 27 casualties in massacres carried out by Russian warplanes and helicopters in Aleppo city] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220214222/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=51049 |date=2016-12-20 }}</ref><ref name="almasdarnews">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-aleppo-launch-offensive/|author=Izat Charkatli|publisher=almasdarnews.com|title=Syrian Army advances in Aleppo after launch of offensive|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427130839/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-aleppo-launch-offensive/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>稍後，親政府的巴勒斯坦民兵攻佔阿勒頗東北部的漢達拉特巴勒斯坦難民營（Handarat Camp）的一部分。<ref name="handarat"/>

9月24日，敘軍進攻南部的Sheikh Sa'id區。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-storm-southern-aleppo-districts/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah storm southern Aleppo districts|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2016-09-24|publisher=|accessdate=2016-09-24|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107091414/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-storm-southern-aleppo-districts/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="storming">{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/single-post/2016/09/24/SAA-Begins-Storming-East-Aleppo|title=SAA Begins Storming East Aleppo!|publisher=The Inside Source|accessdate=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160926063150/http://www.insidesourcenews.com/single-post/2016/09/24/SAA-Begins-Storming-East-Aleppo|archive-date=2016-09-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-attacks-key-district-southern-aleppo/ |title=Syrian Army attacks key district in southern Aleppo |access-date=2016-09-24 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427130829/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-attacks-key-district-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>親政府民兵與政府軍一度攻佔整個漢達拉特難民營，反對派部隊在夜間反攻，奪回該難民營的大部分區域。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sputniknews.cn/military/20160925/1020822196.html |title=叙民兵组织：恐怖分子再次占领阿勒颇东北部哈达拉特难民营 |publisher=俄羅斯衛星網 |date=2016-09-25 |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2016-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928190713/http://sputniknews.cn/military/20160925/1020822196.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

據報9月23日和24日總計有至少55人死於空襲，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/syria-aleppo/3523438.html |title=US, European Allies Say it is Up to Russia to Bring Truce in Syria |publisher=VOA |date=2016-09-25 |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2017-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705205711/https://www.voanews.com/a/syria-aleppo/3523438.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[敘利亞民間防衛團體|敘利亞民防]]阿勒頗分支主席塞爾莫表示有超過100人喪生。<ref name=ltn0925>{{Cite news |url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1035498 |title=敘政府軍進逼阿勒坡 內戰局勢丕變 |work=自由時報電子報 |date=2016-09-25 |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202045040/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1035498 |dead-url=no }}</ref>供應阿勒頗東部反對派控制區自來水的一個抽水站在空襲中被毀，反對派於是關閉供應西部政府軍控制區自來水的另一個抽水站作為報復，東部25萬居民和西部150萬居民的自來水供應受到嚴重影響。<ref name=ltn0925/>

9月25日，親政府民兵與政府軍再次進攻漢達拉特。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/liwaa-al-quds-syrian-army-storm-handarat-camp-northern-aleppo/ |title=Liwaa Al-Quds, Syrian Army storm Handarat Camp in northern Aleppo |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2019-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203055313/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/liwaa-al-quds-syrian-army-storm-handarat-camp-northern-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>據報該日在阿勒頗的戰鬥造成85人喪生。<ref name=cn0926>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-26/8015449.shtml |title=叙利亚冲突再度升级致数百人伤亡 美俄互相指责 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-09-26 |accessdate=2016-09-26 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731225220/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-26/8015449.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月27日，政府軍收復[[阿勒颇城堡|阿勒颇城堡]]以北的法拉菲拉（Farafira）區。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-09/28/c_1119635267.htm |title=叙利亚政府军在阿勒颇战事取得进展 |website=新華網 |date=2016-09-28 |accessdate=2016-10-01 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305063119/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-09/28/c_1119635267.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

美國官員表示在9月19日至27日期間，阿勒頗東部被空襲至少1,700次，造成至少1,000人喪生。<ref name=voa20160930>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voachinese.com/a/us-russia-syria-20160929/3530828.html |title=美国将暂停与俄罗斯在叙利亚问题的外交谈判 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-09-30 |accessdate=2016-09-30 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202045015/https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-russia-syria-20160929/3530828.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月29日，政府軍一方再次攻佔漢達拉特難民營。<ref>[https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/latest-battlefield-map-aleppo-city/ Latest battlefield map of Aleppo City] {{Wayback|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/latest-battlefield-map-aleppo-city/ |date=20180617121709 }}, 2016-09-29</ref>

政府軍一方後來在阿勒頗東部攻佔更多地區。截至10月6日，政府軍已控制布斯坦巴沙（Bustan al-Basha）區超過8成區域。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/point-no-return-islamist-rebels-lose-ground-aleppo-city-map-update/ |title=Point of no return as Islamist rebels lose more ground in Aleppo city - Map update |first=Chris |last=Tomson |date=2016-10-06 |publisher=Al Masdar News |access-date=2016-10-12 |archive-date=2020-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320140539/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/point-no-return-islamist-rebels-lose-ground-aleppo-city-map-update/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

10月10日，「敘利亞人權觀察」表示自9月19日至10月10日期間，阿勒頗有超過500名平民死於空襲和炮轟，大部分是反對派控制區的平民，而政府軍控制的阿勒頗西部也有51名平民死於反對派炮轟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=52034 |title=More than 1800 killed or wounded civilians since the collapse of the American-Russian casefire in Aleppo |publisher=SOHR |date=2016-10-10 |accessdate=2016-10-11 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202044957/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=52034 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==暫時停火==
[[File:AleppoBattle_22Sept_15Oct2016_changes.svg|thumb]]
10月17日，俄羅斯宣佈將於10月20日在東阿勒頗暫停空襲8小時，讓平民與武裝分子撤離。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ft.com/content/829853e4-948f-11e6-a1dc-bdf38d484582|title=Russia and Syria announce eight-hour Aleppo ceasefire|work=Financial Times|date=2016-10-17|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127214846/https://www.ft.com/content/829853e4-948f-11e6-a1dc-bdf38d484582|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來提前兩天暫停空襲，從10月18日早上開始，並維持至次日。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/19/middleeast/syria-aleppo-airstrikes/index.html |title=Syria: Aleppo residents say airstrikes have halted |access-date=2016-10-21 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105846/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/19/middleeast/syria-aleppo-airstrikes/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>10月19日，敘利亞軍方宣佈原定於10月20日實施的日間暫時停火延長至10月22日。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/world/syrian-army-says-aleppo-truce-will-last-three-days_1941706.html |title=Syrian Army says Aleppo truce will last three days |access-date=2016-10-21 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095920/https://zeenews.india.com/news/world/syrian-army-says-aleppo-truce-will-last-three-days_1941706.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然反政府部隊的官員拒絕了撤離阿勒頗的建議，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/russia-urges-other-powers-back-its-ceasefire-aleppo-rebels-reject-withdrawal-905667298|title=Rebels reject withdrawal from Aleppo after Russia halts bombing|work=Middle East Eye|date=2016-10-18|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617093200/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/russia-urges-other-powers-back-its-ceasefire-aleppo-rebels-reject-withdrawal-905667298|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過仍有150名[[自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動|自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動]]的武裝分子選擇撤離，獲安排由巴士接載前往[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/southfront-syrian-army-evacuates-150-islamist-rebels-aleppo-city/|title=SouthFront: Syrian Army evacuates 150 Islamist rebels from Aleppo city|work=Al Masdar News|date=2016-10-19|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202044932/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/southfront-syrian-army-evacuates-150-islamist-rebels-aleppo-city/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==戰鬥恢復==
[[File:Aleppo_rebel_Oct2016_offensive.svg|thumb]]
戰鬥於10月22日恢復。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/10/air-strikes-fighting-mark-aleppo-ceasefire-161022203809648.html|title=Air strikes, fighting mark end of Aleppo ceasefire|publisher=|accessdate=2016-10-30|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809173815/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/10/air-strikes-fighting-mark-aleppo-ceasefire-161022203809648.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>俄羅斯表示俄敘空軍仍會繼續暫停對阿勒頗的空襲，但沒有說明暫停的期限至何時。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-russia-pause-idUSKCN12P26X |title=Russia says it extends moratorium on Aleppo air strikes |date=2016-10-25 |publisher= |accessdate=2016-10-30 |via=Reuters |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111609/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-russia-pause-idUSKCN12P26X |dead-url=no }}</ref>

10月28日，反政府部隊在包圍圈外向阿勒頗西部發動反攻，試圖打破政府軍對東部的包圍。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-37798924|title=Syrian rebels 'start Aleppo offensive'|work=BBC|date=2016-10-28|access-date=2016-11-13|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326235940/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-37798924|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-offensive-idUSKCN12S0QP|title=Syria monitor group says rebel shelling kills more than 15 in west Aleppo|work=Reuters|date=2016-10-28|access-date=2016-11-13|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304174546/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-offensive-idUSKCN12S0QP|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然反政府軍在初期取得少許進展，但最終被政府軍擊退。11月8日，政府軍收復阿勒頗西南部的1070房屋區。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKBN133125 |title=Syrian army says takes Aleppo district, rebels say battle continues |publisher=Reuters |date=2016-11-08 |accessdate=2016-11-13 |archive-date=2021-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210521235241/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKBN133125 |dead-url=no }}</ref>「敘利亞人權觀察」於11月12日宣稱有超過450人在10月28日開始的解圍戰中喪生，包括215名反政府軍、143名政府軍及親政府部隊，以及近100名平民，喪生的平民大多是在政府軍控制的西阿勒頗死於反對派炮火。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/en/assad-regime-erases-gains-by-syrian-rebels-in-aleppo/a-36369565 |title=Assad regime erases gains by Syrian rebels in Aleppo |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-11-12 |accessdate=2016-11-13 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524181933/https://www.dw.com/en/assad-regime-erases-gains-by-syrian-rebels-in-aleppo/a-36369565 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反對派敗退==
11月26日，政府軍收復阿勒頗東部的哈納諾（Hanano）區。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/27/c_1119996553.htm |title=叙利亚政府军收复阿勒颇一重要区域 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-11-27 |accessdate=2016-11-27 |archive-date=2017-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609114911/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/27/c_1119996553.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月27日，Ard Al-Hamra區、賈巴爾巴德羅（Jabal Badro）區和Ayn Al-Tal區也被政府軍收復。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-update-syrian-army-advances-jihadists-mass-retreat-east-aleppo-districts/ |title=Map Update: Syrian Army advances as jihadists mass retreat from east Aleppo districts |date=2016-11-27 |accessdate=2016-11-27 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206003506/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-update-syrian-army-advances-jihadists-mass-retreat-east-aleppo-districts/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voachinese.com/a/syria-20161127/3613460.html |title=叙政府军从反政府力量再夺一地 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-11-28 |accessdate=2016-11-27 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202044850/https://www.voachinese.com/a/syria-20161127/3613460.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月7日，政府軍收復[[阿勒颇古城|阿勒颇古城]]。自從政府軍於9月合圍以來，至此已攻佔包圍圈內反對派控制區大約8成區域。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/2016-12/08/c_1120075463.htm |title=叙利亚政府军收复阿勒颇老城 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-12-08 |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305191731/http://news.xinhuanet.com/2016-12/08/c_1120075463.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

政府軍此後收復更多城區。12月13日，反對派在{{Link-en|奎維克河|Queiq River}}以東的控制區被肅清，只剩下河西的一塊面積約3.5平方公里的區域仍由反對派控制。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/aleppo-rebels-squeezed-syrian-army-retakes-territories-map-update/ |title=Aleppo rebels squeezed as Syrian Army retakes more territories. Map Update |access-date=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116230856/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/aleppo-rebels-squeezed-syrian-army-retakes-territories-map-update/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>同日反對派接受由俄羅斯與土耳其促成的停火協議，同意撤出阿勒頗市。

==反對派撤出==
根據12月13日的協議，該日黃昏後開始停火，然後先讓平民撤出，剩餘的反對派人員和他們的家屬接着撤出，按照原計劃反對派將於12月14日撤離阿勒頗市。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN1421Y9 |title=Syrian rebels say Aleppo truce deal struck, to take effect shortly |accessdate=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713072658/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-ceasefire/syrian-rebels-say-aleppo-truce-deal-struck-to-take-effect-shortly-idUSKBN1421Y9 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/12/syria-rebels-reach-evacuation-deal-government-161213163954322.html |title=Syria rebels reach evacuation deal with government |accessdate=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502000243/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/12/syria-rebels-reach-evacuation-deal-government-161213163954322.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN1420H5 |title=Battle of Aleppo ends after years of fighting as rebels agree to withdraw |accessdate=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713072658/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria/battle-of-aleppo-ends-after-years-of-bloodshed-with-rebel-withdrawal-idUSKBN1420H5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過到12月14日早上，當用作接載撤離者的客車抵達約定地點時，遭到反對派開火攻擊，撤離行動被迫押後。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://sputniknews.com/middleeast/201612141048540120-convoy-aleppo-militants/ |title=Bus Convoy Waiting to Take Last Group of Militants out of Aleppo |publisher=俄羅斯衛星網 |date=2016-12-14 |accessdate=2016-12-14 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202044617/https://sputniknews.com/middleeast/201612141048540120-convoy-aleppo-militants/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>12月15日撤離行動終於開始進行，殘留在包圍圈內的反對派武裝分子約有4,000人，當中約3成屬於[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]，而武裝分子的家屬則有1萬人左右。武裝分子、他們的家屬以及其他不願留下的平民獲安排通過政府軍控制區前往[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]的反對派控制區。<ref name=bbc20161215>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-38329461 |title=Aleppo battle: Evacuation of rebel-held east 'under way' |work=BBC News |date=2016-12-15 |accessdate=2016-12-15 |archive-date=2016-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161215133946/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-38329461 |dead-url=no }}</ref>12月22日，撤離行動結束，總計有至少3萬4千人撤離阿勒頗東部，在最後一批反對派武裝人員與家屬撤離後，政府軍宣佈完全收復阿勒頗。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://cn.rfi.fr/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20161222-%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%86%9B%E9%98%9F%E5%AE%A3%E7%A7%B0%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%94%B6%E5%A4%8D%E9%98%BF%E5%8B%92%E9%A2%87 |title=叙利亚军队宣称全面收复阿勒颇 |publisher=法廣 |date=2016-12-22 |accessdate=2016-12-23 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223081935/http://cn.rfi.fr/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20161222-%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%86%9B%E9%98%9F%E5%AE%A3%E7%A7%B0%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%94%B6%E5%A4%8D%E9%98%BF%E5%8B%92%E9%A2%87 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
